text: Sweden women's national football team () represents Sweden on the women's side in association football. Sweden won the 1984 UEFA European Championship. In the FIFA World Cup, the team ended up second in 2003, and won the bronze medals in 1991 and 2011. ==Other websites== * Sweden women's national team * Sweden women's national team Category:European women's national association football teams Category:Football in Sweden Category:National sports teams of Sweden
